    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan <br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Usagi Clan <br />You are a natural talent when it comes to your clan's characteristics, you gain the following bonuses:</p><ul><li>Your bite and kick attacks crit on a 18 instead of 19 and they increase their ranks to the next tier (1d4-&gt;1d6-&gt;1d8-&gt;1d10-&gt;1d12).</li><li>You gain 1 mastery rank in deception and intimidation.</li><li>Thanks to your big and developed ears you cannot be surprised.</li><li>You gain the Earth Release Mole Movement, but the movement you are allowed is equal to your base walking speed, this jutsu does not count towards the limit of jutsu you know.</li></ul>",
